title: 33: Q2 2017, with Neil Cybart
description: Neil Cybart joins Gartenberg and Ritchie to discuss Apple’s Q2 2017 financial results, including iPhone in and outside of China, iPad mini vs. iPad large screen, Apple Watch and wearables as a business, and more.
